oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Burwell Building
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Thompson Brothers
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Partial view of the Burwell Building. Signs in windows for Lutz Bonds, Loans and American National Insurance Co., Bradstreet. Herbert's Dairy Lunch with Crouch Studio sign on second floor windows. Sign for V.L. Nicholson General Contractor. Poster with Norma Shearer, Riviera Theatre and Joanna, Strand Theatre.
